╚~ Arthur Axford - Sunrise 1921 - D-Day Veteran 1944 - Sunset 2014 ~
Magical memories of fun & laughter, paintings & sunny times. Much loved Dad, Gramps & Special Friend, always smiling in our hearts."═
╩[Bench Back]
In memory of "King" Richard Niazi, whose passion for life
and generosity of spirit was an inspiration to all.

[UNDER SEAT]
A lover of and forever loved by Covent Garden. December 2008"ž
šWALTER LEARY
17th Feb.1920 - 23rd Dec.1994
COUNCILLOR ST.KATHERINE'S WARD 1964-1985
Kingdoms may come, Kingdoms may go
Whatever the end may be
But Old Father Thames keeps rolling along
Down to the mighty sea"▄
